import React from "react";
import { HStack, Link, Box } from "@chakra-ui/react";
import { Link as RouterLink } from "react-router-dom";

export default function Header() {
  return (
    <Box bg="principal.100" px={6} py={4} boxShadow="md">
      <HStack spacing={8}>
        <Link as={RouterLink} to="/dashboard" fontWeight="bold" color="principal.500">
          Dashboard
        </Link>
        <Link as={RouterLink} to="/heatmap" fontWeight="bold" color="principal.500">
          Heatmap
        </Link>
        <Link as={RouterLink} to="/history" fontWeight="bold" color="principal.500">
          Historique
        </Link>
        <Link as={RouterLink} to="/zones" fontWeight="bold" color="principal.500">
          Zones
        </Link>
        <Link as={RouterLink} to="/profile" fontWeight="bold" color="principal.500">
          Profil
        </Link>
        <Link as={RouterLink} to="/login" fontWeight="bold" color="principal.500">
          DÃ©connexion
        </Link>
      </HStack>
    </Box>
  );
}
